Switzerland's most famous raider says he isn't one.Werner K. Rey believes fortunes are made by being friendly
And in little more than a decade of being friendly the 46-year-old Mr. Rey has grown from a modest banker to a billionaire.He achieved this in part with an uncanny talent for getting his foot peacefully in the door of established European companies
