But owning index futures isn't the same as owning the underlying stocks.Stockholders, as a group, can win, because they own a share of corporate earnings, which can grow and boost stock prices
Futures, on the other hand, are a zero sum game -- a market for making side bets about the direction of stock prices. "You don't own anything
