In 1979, however, Westinghouse abandoned the project along with its stake in advanced television.Mr. Brody left the company to find other backers
Mr. Brody left the company to find other backers.He has a claim to the right to commercialize the Westinghouse patents, but he contends that those patents are being infringed by a number of Japanese producers
