Such concerns, however, haven't stopped asset-backed securities from becoming one of Wall Street's hottest new products.Since the spring of 1985, financial alchemists have transformed a wide variety of debt into these new securities
They have sold issues backed by car loans, boat loans and recreational-vehicle loans.They have offered bundles of homeequity loans, as well as packages of loans used to buy vacation time-shares
