investors should consider selling if there has been a fundamental change in a company since they bought its stock.Say you purchased a stock because of a new product that was in the works
Say you purchased a stock because of a new product that was in the works.Now, because of various difficulties, the product has been scrapped
Now, because of various difficulties, the product has been scrapped.Time to sell
