I was driving my truck, stopped at a red light at the corner of Shattuck and Alcatraz at the Oakland-Berkeley border when it hit.Worst part was watching power lines waving above my head and no way to drive away
Was 300 ft. out on a pier in San Rafael.It flopped all around, real dramatic
It flopped all around, real dramatic! Many hairline cracks in the concrete slabs afterwards.Ruined the damn fishing
