For the Politburo replaced Mr. Honecker with a man cut of the same cloth: Egon Krenz, the most recent internal-security chief and a longtime Honecker protege.East Germany, it is clear, is no Poland, where the Communist Party now shares power with the democratically elected Solidarity union
